{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/e694b6e7bca9e695b0e68daee5ba93/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":{"id":"SitePage /posts/e694b6e7bca9e695b0e68daee5ba93/"}},"pageContext":{"url":"/posts/e694b6e7bca9e695b0e68daee5ba93/","relativePath":"posts/e694b6e7bca9e695b0e68daee5ba93.md","relativeDir":"posts","base":"e694b6e7bca9e695b0e68daee5ba93.md","name":"e694b6e7bca9e695b0e68daee5ba93","frontmatter":{"title":"收缩数据库","stackbit_url_path":"posts/e694b6e7bca9e695b0e68daee5ba93","date":"2010-11-13 07:29:00","excerpt":"快速高效的收缩SQL Server数据库的方法，不用写代码，图形界面完成。","comments_count":0,"positive_reactions_count":0,"tags":["SQL Server"],"canonical_url":"https://be-net.azurewebsites.net/post/2010/11/13/e694b6e7bca9e695b0e68daee5ba93","template":"post"},"html":"<p>我的数据库变得越来越大了，可是每次当我收缩数据库时，只变小了一点点而已。后来发现，原来变大的，主要是数据库日志文件。我当时甚至想删除了日志文件，因为不需要那么多日志。可是找了一些方法，什么分离数据库啦，都没什么用。</p>  <p>今天终于从一本书中找到最佳的收缩数据库的方法了，记录一下，备忘。</p>  <p>1）设置数据库模式为简单模式：打开SQL Server企业管理器，在控制台根目录中依次点开Microsoft SQL Server --&gt; SQL Server 组 --&gt; 双击打开你的服务器 --&gt; 双击打开数据库目录 --&gt; 选择数据库名称 --&gt; 然后单击右键选择“属性” --&gt; 选择“选项” --&gt; 在故障还原的模式中选择“简单”，然后按“确定”保存。</p>  <p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_57.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 60.810810810810814%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/dea5374395fb31a8c9c4bfa8f3836257/fcda8/image_thumb_57.png\" srcset=\"/static/dea5374395fb31a8c9c4bfa8f3836257/12f09/image_thumb_57.png 148w,\n/static/dea5374395fb31a8c9c4bfa8f3836257/e4a3f/image_thumb_57.png 295w,\n/static/dea5374395fb31a8c9c4bfa8f3836257/fcda8/image_thumb_57.png 590w,\n/static/dea5374395fb31a8c9c4bfa8f3836257/748f4/image_thumb_57.png 656w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>  <p>2）在当前数据库上单击右键，看所有任务中的“收缩数据库”，一般里面的默认设置不用调整，直接单击“确定”。</p>  <p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_58.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 88.51351351351352%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/e33c1aa761d747f482bbe93a9b892fff/fcda8/image_thumb_58.png\" srcset=\"/static/e33c1aa761d747f482bbe93a9b892fff/12f09/image_thumb_58.png 148w,\n/static/e33c1aa761d747f482bbe93a9b892fff/e4a3f/image_thumb_58.png 295w,\n/static/e33c1aa761d747f482bbe93a9b892fff/fcda8/image_thumb_58.png 590w,\n/static/e33c1aa761d747f482bbe93a9b892fff/374ac/image_thumb_58.png 634w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>  <p>收缩前：（请注意收缩前后的大小变化）</p>  <p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_59.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 81.08108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/df5a04410b62a917eda440a8a90b2982/fcda8/image_thumb_59.png\" srcset=\"/static/df5a04410b62a917eda440a8a90b2982/12f09/image_thumb_59.png 148w,\n/static/df5a04410b62a917eda440a8a90b2982/e4a3f/image_thumb_59.png 295w,\n/static/df5a04410b62a917eda440a8a90b2982/fcda8/image_thumb_59.png 590w,\n/static/df5a04410b62a917eda440a8a90b2982/bce72/image_thumb_59.png 633w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>  <p>收缩后：</p>  <p><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Jeff-Tian/blogengine.net/master/Source/BlogEngine/BlogEngine.NET/App_Data/files/image_60.png\"><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \">\n      <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 81.08108108108108%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"image\" title=\"image\" src=\"/static/754680c07e0b0d39d5287041056ac35b/fcda8/image_thumb_60.png\" srcset=\"/static/754680c07e0b0d39d5287041056ac35b/12f09/image_thumb_60.png 148w,\n/static/754680c07e0b0d39d5287041056ac35b/e4a3f/image_thumb_60.png 295w,\n/static/754680c07e0b0d39d5287041056ac35b/fcda8/image_thumb_60.png 590w,\n/static/754680c07e0b0d39d5287041056ac35b/374ac/image_thumb_60.png 634w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n    </span></a></p>  <p>3）收缩数据库完成后，建议将您的数据库属性重新设置为“完整”模式，操作方法同1）。因为日志在一些异常情况下往往是恢复数据库的重要依据。</p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About","url":"/about","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"关于","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/about","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Contact","url":"/contact","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"Support Me","url":"/support-me","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"叽叽歪歪","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"}],"has_social":true,"social_links":[{"label":"Twitter","url":"https://twitter.com/zizhujy","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-twitter","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Instagram","url":"https://www.instagram.com/jefftian5","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-instagram","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"GitHub","url":"https://github.com/jeff-tian","style":"icon","icon_class":"fa-github","new_window":true,"type":"action"},